      "description": "Codegen is the heart of the compiler. Hindley-Milner inference resolves types, a core generator emits LLVM IR, and feature-specific modules cover effects, fibers, HTTP, iterators, and pattern matching. A dedicated pass enforces exhaustiveness for match expressions.",
